3. Learn practical strategies to build positive habits, manage stress, and enhance overall well-being;
4. Discover ways to foster meaningful relationships and create a supportive social environment; and
5. Develop an action plan to sustain happiness and a sense of fulfillment throughout their university journey and beyond.

